(See also <ref type="internal" target="nbc.divBV2.part9.sect33.subsect5.art3.sent1" display-type="long" pretext="Sentence"/>.)</text>
                  </clause>
                </content>
                <change-summary>Repealed and substituted Sentence 9.33.5.2.(1) with new clauses (a) through (g) for installation standards</change-summary>
                <note>Ministerial Order BA 2024 02</note>
